近日，作为新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情的主要捐赠渠道，湖北省及各级红十字会再次站在了舆论风暴之中。
Recently, as the new coronavirus pneumonia major donor channel, Hubei Province and the Red Cross at all levels once again stood in the storm of public opinion.
疫情爆发以来，社会各界源源不断捐赠湖北，与此同时，前线医院却纷纷在社交媒体上呐喊物资告急，大众不禁发问，我捐的钱用上了吗？给谁用了？这些信息能去哪里看？就此，南都记者对湖北省及其下辖的17个市（州）（包含12个地级市、1个自治州、3个省直辖县级市、1个省直辖林区）红十字会官方公示的防疫捐赠信息进行了梳理。
Since the outbreak of the outbreak, the community has been donated to Hubei, but at the same time, the front-line hospitals on social media, the public can not help but ask, I donated money to whom? Where can the information be seen? Hubei Province and 17 cities (counties) including 12 prefectures, 3 provincial municipal governments, 1 provincial directly administered forest areas) Red Cross official publicity information.
多地红会捐赠金额统计混乱，省红会单日数据差额达两千余万为更好了解湖北省及下属17个市（州）红十字会募捐和物资发放情况，南都记者查询了截止到2020年1月31日，各地红十字会两微一端、以及包括地方人民政府官网、卫健委官网、政务平台等等在内其他官方渠道（以公示明细为准，新闻稿不计入，5小时以上都无法查询到，即查询难度极高的不计入）的公示信息。
In order to better understand the collection and distribution of materials by the Red Cross Society of Hubei Province and its 17 cities (states), the Southern Red Cross Society inquired about other official channels as of January 31, 2020.
抗击疫情之际，社会各界慷慨解囊。
When fighting the epidemic, all sectors of society generously contributed.
作为首府、是疫情“第一线”，武汉市受到举国关注，收到捐款高达6.189亿。
As the capital and the "first line" of the epidemic, Wuhan city has attracted the attention of the whole country and received 618.9 million donations.
居次的是黄冈市红十字会，收到约6175万捐款，排第三的孝感市红十字会，收到约4389.8万元捐款。
In second place was the Huanggang Red Cross, which received about 61.75 million donations, ranking third in the filial piety city Red Cross, receiving about $43.898 million in donations.
接下来襄阳市、随州市、荆州市、荆门市和鄂州市等地红十字会，均获得千万捐款。
Next Xiangyang City, Suizhou City, Jingzhou City, Jingmen City and Huizhou Red Cross Society, all received tens of millions of donations.
值得注意的是，还有五地红十字会没有社会捐款公示，分别为恩施州、天门市、潜江市、神农架林区、黄石市。
It is worth noting that five other Red Cross societies have no public donations: Enshi, Tianmen, Qianjiang, Shennongshan and Huangshi.
通过对比公开数字，南都记者注意到，湖北省确诊病例分布和各地红十字会收到捐款数额排名有很高重合度，各地确诊病例也大致按照这一顺序排列。
By comparing public figures, Nan noted that the distribution of confirmed cases in Hubei Province and the number of donations received by the Red Cross Societies all over the country coincide in a high degree, and confirmed cases in different places follow roughly the same order.
不过南都记者发现，有些红十字会还存在公布数字口径不一致、公示表格格式不统一等问题，很容易让公众在理解上产生混乱。
However, Southern journalists have found that some Red Cross societies still have problems with the publication of inconsistent digital calibres and inconsistent formats of public display forms, which can easily lead to confusion in public understanding.
比如，湖北省红十字会在《捐赠情况公布（一）》中写到，“截止25日16时，全省红十字系统共募集捐款3162.28万元”，但是在其附件表格“2020年1月25日新型肺炎捐款信息公示”中，却显示募集捐款总金额为"3482232.11"元，相差了近2814万元。
For example, the Red Cross Society of Hubei Province said in its Report on Donations (1): "As of 16: 00 pm yesterday, the provincial Red Cross system had collected 31,628,800 yuan," but its attached form, "Information on New Pneumonia Donation on January 25, 2020," shows that the total amount collected was & quot; 3482232.11 & quot; & quot; & quot;
因为该附件表格未标明具体的截止时间以及涵盖范围（只是省红十字，还是全省累加），很容易让公众产生误解，而且类似问题在其他几个公告中同样存在。
Since the annex table does not indicate specific deadlines and coverage (provincial Red Cross or province-wide), it is easy for the public to misunderstand and similar issues exist in several other bulletins.
11城红十字会公示信息未提及资金、物品具体流向除了捐赠信息公开外，物资及资金的明细使用和去向同样是社会关注的重点话题。
In addition to the disclosure of donation information, the detailed use and destination of materials and funds are also important topics of concern to the society.
1月30日，“武汉协和医院医疗物资不是告急，而是即将全部用尽”的新闻引发广泛关注。
January 30, "Wuhan Concorde Hospital medical supplies are not urgent, but will soon be exhausted" the news caused widespread concern.
同日，湖北省红十字会第一次公布了本次疫情以来该会接收捐赠物资使用情况，其中，口罩等物资流向“不合理”和捐赠数量“合不上”等问题，引发公众质疑。
On the same day, the Red Cross Society of Hubei Province announced for the first time that it had received donations since the outbreak, raising questions about the flow of materials such as masks to "unreasonable" and "inadequate" donations.
根据公示信息，南都记者发现，截止1月31日，仅有湖北省、武汉市、荆州市、孝感市、鄂州市5个红十字会明确列出了社会捐赠物资及资金的去向，也就是具体划拨给了哪些医院或机构。
As of January 31, only five Red Cross Societies in Hubei, Wuhan, Jingzhou, Xiaogan City and Huzhou had clearly listed where the donations and funds had gone, i.e. to which hospitals or institutions, according to public information.
另外，襄阳市红十字会列出了捐款使用的明细，也就是用捐款购买了哪些物资（未列出划拨给了哪些医院或机构）。
In addition, the Xiangyang City Red Cross gave a breakdown of the use of the contributions, i.e., which items were purchased with donations (without indicating which hospitals or institutions were allocated).
其中，武汉市、孝感市、荆州市、襄阳市四地红十字会在公示中提及资金流向。
Among them, Wuhan, Xiaogan City, Jingzhou, Xiangyang City, the Red Cross in four places mentioned in the public flow of funds.
孝感市红十字会拨付金额占到获捐金额11.48%，襄阳市占28%，武汉市占29.66%，荆州市占比最高，为46.04%。
The Red Cross allocated 11.48 percent of the donations, Xiangyang 28 percent, Wuhan 29.66 percent and Jingzhou 46.04 percent.
剩余的11个红十字会只提及了捐赠情况。
The remaining 11 Red Cross societies referred only to donations.
比如，随州市红十字会在1月31日公布的《随州市红十字会关于接受社会捐赠资金及医疗物资的情况公示(四)》中，只提及了31个单位或个人捐款的时间、金额，以及30日17时至31日17时累计接受捐款的总额，没有对任何支出和划拨给医院的物资或款项进行说明。
For example, the Red Cross Society of Suizhou City, in its Circular (IV) on the Receipt of Donations and Medical Materials by the Red Cross Society of Suizhou City, published on January 31, refers only to the time and amount of donations from 31 units or individuals and the total amount of contributions received from 1700 hours to 1700 hours on the 30th.
至于最近处于舆论风口浪尖上的湖北省红十字会，南都记者注意到，自1月25日开始，湖北省红十字会开始在官网对外公布捐赠情况，截至2月1日，总计公布七次。
As for the Red Cross Society of Hubei Province, which has been in the hot seat of public opinion recently, Nan noted that since January 25, the Red Cross Society of Hubei Province has been publishing donations on official websites.
其中，附有详细捐赠信息的电子表格共计六次（《捐赠情况公布（四）》中未见有详细捐赠信息的电子表格），公开了受捐款项，但没有捐款使用及流向。
Of these, a total of six spreadsheets with detailed information on donations (spreadsheets with detailed donation information are not available in Publish of Donations (IV)), where contributions are disclosed, but no use is made of them and where they flow.
直到1月30日，湖北省红十字会第一次公布了部分捐赠物资使用情况，距离第一次公布捐赠情况已经过去了五天。
Until January 30, the Red Cross Society of Hubei Province announced the use of some donations for the first time, five days after the first announcement.
湖北省委副书记、武汉市市委书记马国强在1月31日晚接受《新闻1+1》主播白岩松采访时表示，将责成慈善机构每三天发布接受捐赠的情况、捐赠物品使用的去向。
In an interview with Bai Yansong, deputy secretary of the Hubei Provincial Communist Party and head of Wuhan Municipal Party Committee, Ma Guoqiang told News 1 + 1 on the evening of January 31 that charities would be required to publish every three days on the status of donations and where they are being used.
南都记者整理官网信息发现，在湖北当地的17个红十字会（潜江市红十字会没有官方捐赠信息公布）中，间隔三天以上才公示捐赠情况的现象较为普遍，鄂州市曾经实现过当天获捐当天公布，但也有拖延三四天才公布的记录。
In Hubei, 17 Red Cross Societies (the city's Red Cross has no official donation information), donations were announced more than three days apart, according to a report published on the same day, but there were also records of delays of three or four days.
荆门市红十字会表现最差，出现31日才补录24日的几例捐赠信息的情况，间隔了七天。
The Red Cross in Jingmen City was the worst performer, after a seven-day hiatus in recording a few donations on the 24th.
整体来看，捐赠信息公布最及时的是武汉市、黄冈市和荆州市红十字会，没有超过两天。
Overall, the most timely release of donation information is Wuhan, Huanggang City and Jingzhou Red Cross, no more than two days.
6家红十字会官方传播渠道“三无”信息查询需辗转多个渠道社会捐助信息公示工作是慈善工作的重要环节，早在2009年，汶川地震诈捐、虚捐等风波出现后，民政部就曾发布《关于进一步加强社会捐助信息公示工作的指导意见》。
As early as 2009, the Ministry of Civil Affairs issued the "Guidelines on Further Strengthening the Publicity of Information on Social Donations" after six official Red Cross channels had to turn over multiple channels to publicize information on social donations.
红十字会作为公益机构，建立起统一的媒介平台作为公示渠道，让捐赠人随时了解善款管理使用的情况十分必要。
As a public welfare organization, the Red Cross has established a unified media platform as a publicity channel to keep donors informed of the use of charitable fund management.
南都记者发现，湖北省包括17个市（州）的红十字会中有10个没有官方网站，其中随州市、孝感市、荆门市三地在目前公示出来的捐赠款项中，收入均超过一千万。
Ten of the Red Cross Societies in Hubei Province, including 17 cities, do not have official websites, including Suizhou, Xiaogan City and Jingmen City, which have more than 10 million yuan in their current donations, according to Nan Du reporter.
在这10个没有官网的红十字会中，有3个将捐赠信息公示在了当地人民政府网站或者卫健委官网，但仍有包括荆门市、黄石市、咸宁市、仙桃市、天门市、潜江市、神农架林区在内的7个红十字会没有任何官方网站公示信息。
Of the 10 Red Cross societies without official networks, three have posted donation information on local people's government websites or the Wei Yuan network, but seven, including Jingmen City, Huangshi City, Xianning City, Xiantao City, Tianmen City, Qianjiang City, Shennongjiang City and Shennong Forest Area have no official website.
虽然有一些红十字会开通官方微信公众号或微博账号，但账号属于“僵尸账号”，没有公示捐赠信息，相当于没有起到信息公开、供社会舆论监督的作用。
Although some Red Cross societies open official micro-public or micro-blog accounts, but account numbers belong to "zombie accounts", do not disclose donation information, equivalent to the role of information open, for public opinion oversight role.
以鄂州市红十字会为例，鄂州市红十字会微信公众号“博爱鄂州”，自1月25日发布接受捐款推文后，也再没有任何更新。
Taking the Huzhou Red Cross as an example, the Huizhou Red Cross Society micro-letter public "fraternity Huizhou" has not been updated since January 25 after the announcement of the acceptance tweets.
此外，其新浪微博账号没有进行官方认证，拥有24个粉丝。
In addition, its Sina Weibo account is not officially certified and has 24 fans.
南都记者注意到，该微博在1月26日、1月29日和1月31日分别发布社会捐赠明细情况（一）（二）（四），捐赠明细文件加盖当地红十字会公章。
Nandu reporter noted that the micro-blog on January 26, 29 January and 31, respectively, issued a breakdown of social donations (i) (ii) (iv), donation of detailed documents stamped with the local Red Cross official seal.
不过，社会捐赠明细情况（一）的链接内容为社会捐赠明细情况（二）。
However, the social donation details (i) of the link for the social donation details (ii).
最后，南都记者辗转多个渠道，终于在“云上鄂州”（鄂州政务网站）查询到完整捐赠公示信息。
Finally, the Southern reporter toss and turn a number of channels, finally in the "cloud above Huzhou" (Huizhou government website) to find the complete donation publicity information.
再如新浪微博@黄冈市红十字会，唯一一条博文发于2015年7月28日，“黄冈市红十字会微博开通了。
Again, like Sina Weibo @ Huanggang City Red Cross, the only blog posted on July 28, 2015, "Huanggang City Red Cross Weibo opened.
欢迎大家关注。
Your attention is welcome.
”特别需要指出的是，没有建设两微一端“三无”红十字会有6家，分别为随州市区、仙桃市、黄石市、恩施州、天门市、潜江市。
In particular, there are six Red Cross Societies, one in Suizhou, one in Xiantao, one in Huangshi, one in Enshi, one in Tianmen, and one in submerged river.
南都记者注意到，最近登上微博热搜榜的杭州红十字会，多渠道公示信息的做法值得借鉴。
Nandu reporter noted that recently boarded the Weibo hot search of the Hangzhou Red Cross, multi-channel publicity practices worth learning.
1月31日，杭州红十字会常务副会长魏丹英在新闻发布会上表示，为了更好使用和方便社会监督，杭州红十字会从1月28日起在《杭州日报》第四版登报公示每日捐赠物款收入和支出情况，并同步更新官网和微信公众号，还将通过电视滚动播放公示。
On January 31, the Hangzhou Red Cross, vice-president of the Red Cross Society Wei Dan-ying, told a news conference that the Hangzhou Red Cross began publishing daily donations of goods and expenditure in the fourth edition of Hangzhou Daily on January 28.
值得一提的是，不少网友从这份报纸公示中发现“杭州保姆纵火案”当事人林生斌先生于1月28日捐赠价值为9万元的5000只口罩。
It is worth mentioning that many netizens have found out from this newspaper that Lin Shengbin, a party to the "Hangzhou Nanny case," donated 5,000 masks worth 90,000 yuan on January 28.
校友会、后援会纷纷晒表格、附图片、列明细，打消质疑除了红十字会外，不少民间组织也发起了募捐。
Alumni associations, aid committees have basked in forms, pictures and details to dispel doubts that, in addition to the Red Cross, many non-governmental organizations have also launched fund-raising.
那么他们又是如何进行物资使用说明，解答捐赠者的疑惑？南都记者了解到，武汉大学深圳校友会从1月29日起，每天通过微信推送关于捐款和支出明细的文章，逐项列出捐款者、金额、捐款物品、采购物品、数量、去向和物流等问题。
Since January 29, the Shenzhen Alumni Association of Wuhan University has been sending detailed articles on donations and expenditures by micromail, itemizing the contributors, amounts, donations, items procured, quantity, destination and logistics.
针对物流配送这一备受关注的问题，他们写明每一笔物资属于发出、在途还是送达，并附上物资发出图片予以佐证。
In response to the concern about logistics, they stated whether each item was shipped, in transit or delivered, supported by pictures of the materiel being sent.
由于捐款数据庞大，微信推文中还附上网盘地址，供公众查询所有捐款明细。
Due to the size of the donation data, the tweets are accompanied by an address on the dashboard for public access to a breakdown of all donations.
此外，武大深圳校友会除了列明医院所需物资须符合的标准，还提供一名志愿者的微信二维码，为捐赠者提供标准物资进行指引，避免浪费资源。
In addition, the HKU Shenzhen Alumni Association provides a two-dimensional microcode of a volunteer to guide donors in the provision of standard materials to avoid wasting resources, in addition to setting out the standards to be met by hospitals.
这场牵动全国民众的防疫捐赠行动，“饭圈女孩”也没有缺席。
The "Dining-Circle Girl" was not absent from the donation campaign, which affected the whole country.
南都记者注意到，1月26日，朱一龙粉丝通过微博@Loong_朱一龙公益个站，发起了向湖北部分医院捐赠医用手套的活动。
Nandu reporters noted that on January 26, Zhu Yilong fans through Weibo @ Loong _ Zhu Yilong Volunteer Station launched the donation of medical gloves to some hospitals in Hubei Province.
该个站先是联系到手套生产厂商，再通过第三方平台募捐16.4万元用于手套生产和运输。
The station first contacted the glove manufacturer and raised 164,000 yuan for glove production and transportation through a third party platform.
期间，有粉丝就捐款提出质疑，“Loong_朱一龙公益个站”特地整理粉丝关心的善款使用、手套单价、厂家资质、物资捐赠分配、发货时间、物流配送等问题，统一发博作出详细解释。
During this period, fans raised questions about the donation, "Loong _ Zhu Yilong public welfare station" specially collated the use of donations, gloves unit price, manufacturers qualifications, material donation distribution, delivery time, logistics and other issues, the unified distribution Booth to make a detailed explanation.
此外，该个站不断更新手套的运输情况，并附上多张现场图片让粉丝放心。
In addition, the station continuously updated the transport of gloves, and attached a number of live pictures to reassure fans.
据该个站1月31日微博，第一批医用外科手术手套于1月30日凌晨抵达黄冈，当地指挥部已经通知医院前往领取，第二批一次性检查手套也已装车运输。
The first medical surgical gloves arrived in Huanggang in the early morning hours of 30 January, according to Weibo, where the local command had informed the hospital to collect them and a second batch of disposable gloves had been loaded for transport.
